			</varlistentry>
			<varlistentry>
				<term><emphasis>Returns</emphasis>&nbsp;:</term>
				<listitem><simpara>A new 
						<link linkend="class-canvas-points"><classname>goocanvas.Points</classname></link>
					</simpara></listitem>
			</varlistentry>
		</variablelist>
		<para>
			Creates a new canvas points item.
		</para>
		<para>
			Here's an example showing how to create points.
